{
  "stem": "13693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so they killed them in Ponary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I remained, myself and the younger brother, still alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gershon.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it started a struggle-- no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the thing is, it's very-- I'm very-- we have to make a-- we have to find a way of be able to support ourselves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the thing is, we got first my brother joined the Brogansky, what was working for the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was working for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was, at that time, probably 13-- 12 or 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was working in different job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the only way we could survive is to bring in from the outside, bring in some food-- food, or food stuff, to the ghetto, and sell at a higher price.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the life is where-- it's rough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every single day, every couple days, the German are demanding people for Ponary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's a continuous so-called [NON-ENGLISH], or action, under the name [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They use a pseudonym.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They use-- they use different watershed so-called [NON-ENGLISH], to transfer to a different place of work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Euphemisms.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But really, they took them to the Ponary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the stories happened-- one of the things happened during the yellow shines.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jews built, in order to survive, and to be-- to save themself from the deportation, they had to hide themselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was in the beginning, when the idea was to hide, and to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our philosophy, for ages, was with our superior spiritual value, mind, intelligence, we can maybe survive over ages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was no match for the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The cruelty-- there was no-- there was no-- no-- there was only the murderous, a philosophy of destruction, of genocide.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And against it there was no-- no fight or wisdom.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
